{"id":"5e9c2bbe9b6559241525d5ad","title":"New: Love, Dance – Bergen, Again","content":"<p>Remember when <strong>The Drums</strong> were relevant, and almost perfected the art of ‘cutesy indie-pop’? This new track from <a href=\"https://www.</p><p>facebook.com/pages/Love-Dance-official/152334838115398?sk=wall\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Love, Dance</strong></a> sort of reminds me of those times, before <strong>Johnny Pierce</strong> thought he was <strong>Morrissey</strong> and began acting like an arsehole. Anyway, <em>Bergen, Again</em> is a sugary sweet indie-pop gem, taking fairly noticeable inspiration from <strong>The Cure</strong> and <strong>The Smiths</strong>, as well as a slight whiff of <strong>Pale Saints</strong>. With more songs in the works, I’m pretty excited to hear what<strong> Love, Dance</strong> are going to come up with next, so, as they themselves brilliantly paraphrase <strong>Notorious B.I.G.</strong> in the final lines of <em>Bergen, Again</em>, ‘<em>if you don’t know, now you know</em>‘.</p>\n<p><object width=\"100%\" height=\"81\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" codebase=\"https://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><param name=\"src\" value=\"https://player.soundcloud.com/player.swf?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F32948789\" /><embed width=\"100%\" height=\"81\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" src=\"https://player.soundcloud.com/player.swf?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F32948789\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" /></object> <span><a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/increasethepeace/love-dance-bergen-again\">Love Dance – Bergen, again</a> by <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/increasethepeace\">IncreaseThePeace</a></span></p>\n","slug":"13721-new-love-dance-bergen-again","category":"introducing","date":1326383071000,"wpid":13721,"isSticky":false,"featured_image":{"width":165,"height":165,"sr